items.name: Ford Australia Wiki
items.title: Ford Australia Wiki
items.headline: Ford Australia Wiki
items.desc: This Wiki is about vehicles that were either produced in Australia or were official imports to Australia. It was created to form one area of knowledge about these unique vehicles that exist in Australia and nowhere else. It covers unique vehicles such as the Ford Ute which was an Australian invention to the problem on how you can have a car to drive to church on Sunday and take the pigs to market on Monday (Aussies will get where this comes from) to the legendary Ford GTHO, in the 70's was the fastest 4 door production car in the world. It also covers modern vehicles and contemporary models like the Ford Falcon XR8 / XR6 Turbo and Ford Performance Vehicles (FPV)

   * To expose the wingnuts currently infesting Australian politics.
